---

<div
	id="about"
	class="relative z-10 w-full bg-white transition-colors duration-300 dark:bg-slate-900"
>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="grid items-start gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div>
				<h2
					class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
				>
					I bring order to creative chaos.
				</h2>
				<div
					class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-500"
				>
					<p>
						I am a creative and results-driven <strong
							>Marketing Project Manager</strong
						> with over 10 years in creative operations and product management.
					</p>
					<p>
						I specialize in regulated and healthcare-adjacent environments (FCC,
						CE, FDA), using structured processes to maintain compliance without
						killing creativity. I lead cross-functional teams to deliver
						multi-channel campaigns on time, on budget, and on brand.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-8">
					<button
						class="nav-link inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-3 rounded-full border border-transparent bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-white focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900"
						data-target="resume"
					>
						View Full Resume
						<svg
							class="h-4 w-4"
							xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
							width="24"
							height="24"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
						>
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div
				class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 p-8 transition-colors duration-300 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800"
			>
				<h3 class="mb-6 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
					Core Competencies
				</h3>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<span
						class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200"
						>Creative Project Leadership</span
					>
					<span
						class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200"
						>Agency Management</span
					>
					<span
						class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200"
						>Budget Tracking ($250k+)</span
					>
					<span
						class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200"
						>Workfront & Jira</span
					>
					<span
						class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200"
						>Proposal (RFP) Management</span
					>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-8 border-t border-slate-200 pt-8 dark:border-slate-700">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
						My Tech Stack
					</h3>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
						<div
							class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
						>
							<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								><path
									d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.21-1.96 1.08-3.11-1.06.05-2.31.71-3.06 1.48-.69.7-1.24 1.85-1.09 2.98 1.18.08 2.36-.51 3.07-1.35"
								></path></svg
							>
							MacBook Pro
						</div>
						<div
							class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
						>
							<svg
								class="h-4 w-4"
								fill="none"
								stroke="currentColor"
								viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								><path
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									stroke-width="2"
									d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg
							>
							AI Tools
						</div>
						<div
							class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
						>
							<svg
								class="h-4 w-4"
								fill="none"
								stroke="currentColor"
								viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								><path
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									stroke-width="2"
									d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
								></path></svg
							>
							Notion
						</div>
						<div
							class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
						>
							<svg
								class="h-4 w-4"
								fill="none"
								stroke="currentColor"
								viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								><path
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									stroke-width="2"
									d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"
								></path></svg
							>
							Workfront
						</div>
						<div
							class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
						>
							<svg
								class="h-4 w-4"
								fill="none"
								stroke="currentColor"
								viewBox="0 0 24 24"
								><path
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									stroke-width="2"
									d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"
								></path></svg
							>
							Standing Desk
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
